{"tid":1629370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：四年前的預告，今日兌現。","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T08:57:54.000Z","uid":69753,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf28bcb9fc690f4d84caf9e2be9a3500f4ad4764","tid":1629370,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"6 October 2015<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：李嘉誠捱批鬥，曾蔭權被逮捕，香港本土的上流社會被逼選擇城邦論！過去，中共的殖民以低下層和中層着手，派遣雙非人、走私客來對付低下層，派遣留學生、海歸派專業人士來對付中層。上層的資本排斥和司法壓迫，現在開始了，而且以重頭戲來開始，攻堅、打大老虎，這是中共的常用戰略&mdash;&mdash;打下層，是無聲無色；打高層，是風風火火。<span style=\"color: red;\">李嘉誠捱批鬥，曾蔭權受到司法滋擾</span>。英國殖民時代留下的高官、專業人士和資本家，現在的政治抉擇，就擺在你們面前。你們選擇城邦論，中共會忌憚，放你們一條生路。你們選擇親共，死路一條（許仕仁、曾蔭權是例子）；選擇逃亡香港，也是死路一條，<span style=\"color: red;\">港共政府會用司法引渡，將你們抓回來。</span><br />\n在香港，我最了解中共了。在中共面前要生存，你要成為他可怕的敵人（formidable enemy）。向中共下跪，輸降納幣，遲早也被砍頭。"},{"pid":"878d7dfd86c7ec2fa687b275a92d2db5f1d84a0e","tid":1629370,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"老師又中<br />\n究竟有怎樣的學識和遠見才可以做到老師那樣"},{"pid":"f5bde07551ffa0a64c9d9f47b7be31aafc0fd68c","tid":1629370,"uid":225050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀，食藥喇夠鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e1e4fae54d2465070fd175e6183e4758f44052","tid":1629370,"uid":224967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"老師英明！<br />\n<br />\n真乖。"},{"pid":"c0c14ac2c485d320d36c1dc221c8f4dbc8595b5a","tid":1629370,"uid":171829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"878d7dfd86c7ec2fa687b275a92d2db5f1d84a0e","tid":1629370,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"老師又中<br />\n究竟有怎樣的學識和遠見才可以做到老師那樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"準時食藥應該可以 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a865d0c0caa5cd8558078a4764437d9b4d9ed6c0","tid":1629370,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7393c73042767feeff3b7d7d449bbbd82178f6f7","tid":1629370,"uid":43777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢同689一9樣日日刷存在感"},{"pid":"6bf4613e7eadc1e1d6140cde2b57dc0dd9065b81","tid":1629370,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"e8789ce7ddbe71f64b7ac29e69412d0b193b20ec","tid":1629370,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今日香港繼續戒嚴吧。請深層國家今日繼續維持本地財閥商場及連鎖店關閉，公共交通有限服務，安排中國國企及紅色資本家受襲，為香港元首創造動亂條件，推出更多緊急法，搞亂香港，幫美國跨國大鱷金融洗劫香港，交付費用，之後香港普選自治建國。"},{"pid":"3c5ae56844df690db1e3abf2d0d3fec77a3adbaa","tid":1629370,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3db94adb4b8f7d057cc6181fe0e18d3afcc3f9b","tid":1629370,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgyZkkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgyZkkM.jpg&h=ffe1f0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 陳雲在此，天滅中共，全黨死清光！"}]}